history.content:
October 19th 5-8 PM


The IEEE Careers in Software Networking Nights intends to focus on individual or small group sessions in which you can discuss your resume, background, teams that you fit in that company and so more! You can register from https://ieee-eecs-careerfair.i3e.dev/register. We will send an email to everyone sign up as the time slots will be available for companies. You would be able to meet with engineers and recruiters from General Motors, Visa, and Roblox virtually, and sign up to meet with Intel representatives in person in Wozniak Lounge.
